OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfsted boss rejects calls  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto pause inspections       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Stopping or preventing school          
OL,6, inspections in England would be against
OL,7, "children's best interests", the chief 
OL,8, inspector of Ofsted has said.          
OL,10,FTeachers have called for them to be    
OL,11,Fpaused, after head teacher Ruth Perry  
OL,12,Ftook her own life while waiting for a  
OL,13,Freport that downgraded her school.     
OL,15,FIn the outcry since her death, some    
OL,16,Fteachers have worn black armbands      
OL,17,Fduring inspections in tribute to her.  
OL,19,FAmanda Spielman said inspections are   
OL,20,Fimportant for both schools and parents.
